  "text": "The part of the boundary state |B gh in the ghost sector is identical to the one constructed for Dp-branes in ten dimensional superstring theory [23, [CITATION_1] . The sum denoted by α above will run over the periodicity (namely the NS-NS and R-R sectors) and spin structures (which encode how the left and right fermions are glued together for a given periodicity).",
